Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
